metadata.dci:title: Wikipedia Top 25 Report, February 17-23, 2013
metadata.dci:creator: Lily Woodard
Joe Lollo
metadata.dci:description: Wikipedia's Top 25 Report from February 17 to 23, 2013, indicating the most viewed pages from that date and matched with . Pages include the Harlem Shake dance craze, recently deceased artist Edward Gorey, and topical television series including House of Cards and The Walking Dead.
metadata.ddi:dataProcessing: Data was gathered from a published Top 25 Report on Wikipedia using Tabula, and cleaned for machine-readability using OpenRefine.
